Procedure to migrate mysql from one Disk space to another
1. move /var/lib/mysql to the new disk path (e.g. /data/mysql)
2. Modify mysql.conf file to change the data dir from /var/lib/mysql to /data/mysql

Error: MySQL won't start after changing the datadir (14.04, mysql 5.7)
Solution: https://askubuntu.com/questions/758898/mysql-wont-start-after-changing-the-datadir-14-04-mysql-5-7
